data.description: If you're looking for the perfect home for entertaining then make the appointment and check this one out! This home has it all!! There are two primary bedrooms, one on the main floor with a private screened porch and the other on the second floor with a private deck. Both bedrooms have jetted tubs. The bamboo floors are beautiful!! The kitchen has beautiful custom cabinetry with a Jenn-Air stove. There is a great office space with built-ins. The game room has a beautiful herringbone floor. The theater has tiered floors with custom lighting. There is a Nest thermostat and the home is also wired for an alarm system. There is an outside shower and outside elevator which will support up to 1000 pounds with security gate. The inground irrigation system will keep your yard looking beautiful and green! There are also hurricane shutters.  There are 2 HVAC units, The second floor unit is new in 2023. The decks have also been stained in 2023.  The dryer vent was recently cleaned as well.  Enjoy the sound view from the front porch or enjoy the privacy from the back deck. This home truly is something to see!!
